---
// about.astro
---
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Libre+Baskerville:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Inter:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
		<title>About | Niina Pollari</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<main>
			<header class="site-header">
				<h1>NIINA POLLARI</h1>
			</header>

			<nav class="top-nav">
				<ul>
					<li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
					<li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
					<li><a href="/books">Books</a></li>
					<li><a href="/other-writing">Other Writing</a></li>
					<li><a href="https://sadreview.substack.com">Newsletter</a></li>
					<li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
				</ul>
			</nav>

			<section class="content-page">
				<h2>About</h2>
				<div class="about-grid">
					<div class="profile-photo">
						<img src="/niina1.jpg" alt="Niina Pollari" />
					</div>
					<div class="bio-text">
						<p>Niina Pollari is the author of two poetry collections, <i>Path of Totality</i> (Soft Skull 2022) and <i>Dead Horse</i> (Birds, LLC 2015). She is also the translator, from the Finnish, of Tytti Heikkinen's selected collection, <i>The Warmth of the Taxidermied Animal</i>. Her next collection, <i>Risk Tolerance</i>, will be out from Autofocus Books in early 2027. She is represented by Monika Ostrowska of Triangle House. </p>
                        <p> Contact Niina at: <b>niina dot pollari at gmail dot com.</b></p>

					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<style>
			/* 1. GLOBAL STYLES */
			* { box-sizing: border-box; }
			body { 
				margin: 0; 
				padding: 0; 
				background-color: #fdfdfd; 
				color: #1a1a1a;
				font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', serif;
			}
			main { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; }

			/* 2. HEADER & NAV */
			.site-header { text-align: center; padding: 5rem 0 2.5rem; }
			.site-header h1 { font-size: 3.2rem; letter-spacing: 0.3rem; font-weight: normal; margin: 0; }
			
			.top-nav { border-top: 1px solid #eee; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; margin-bottom: 5rem; padding: 1.2rem 0; }
			.top-nav ul { list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 3rem; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
			.top-nav a { text-decoration: none; color: #777; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; }
			.top-nav a:hover { color: #000; }

			/* 3. THE ABOUT GRID & PHOTO RESIZING */
			.content-page h2 { font-weight: normal; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
			
			.about-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: 350px 1fr; /* This keeps the photo at 350px */
				gap: 4rem;
				align-items: start;
				margin-bottom: 5rem;
			}

			.profile-photo img {
				width: 100%; /* Fills the 350px column exactly */
				height: auto;
				box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
			}

			.bio-text { line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.1rem; }

			/* 4. MOBILE STYLES */
			@media (max-width: 850px) {
				.about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; text-align: center; }
				.profile-photo img { max-width: 280px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
			}
		</style>
	</body>
</html>